Walter Ezequiel Matthysse Jr (born July 8, 1998) is an Argentine boxer who was an amateur world champion of the WBC middleweight in 2018. He is the son of Walter Matthysse Sr. who is a former professional boxer and nephew of Lucas Matthysse a former professional boxer.
